name: AnimeChar - Railgun Mix | Shirai Kuroko (白井 黑子)
description:
UPDATED [20230603]:

I just replaced some datasets and adjusted some parameters for better image quality. However, please note that all sample images have not been processed by Hires. fix. Please feel free to apply it if you want higher resolution images.

I may try to train a clothing model in the future, but I can't make any promises ;) .

Greetings to all,

We are pleased to announce the launch of our new series, Railgun Mix, which is part of AnimeChar. Our aim is to generate a specific character using Lora based on our extensive dataset.

In this series, we would like to introduce our newly trained Lora model of Shirai Kuroko (白井 黑子), Mikoto's best friend, partner, and roommate.

Trigger words: shirai_kuroko, twintails, [Optional: brown eyes]
** If you want to a long hair without twintails style, please add (twintails), (bow), (hair bow) in negative prompts.


You may buy me a drink to support my work ^v^ : https://www.buymeacoffee.com/ryalandai
My instagram for ai painting and model updates: https://www.instagram.com/rya.land.ai
Also, you welcome to give 5 stars to the model.

Please check "About this version" to know more details about the model version and included characters. The model base is Anything v4.0.

-- Please also support --

AnimeChar - Railgun Mix

Misaka Mikoto (御坂 美琴)
